item.title: Skyjacks: Episode 205
item.description: Orimar, Jonnit, and Gable explore Sorrow's End. They run into a thoroughly unpleasant Readfeather official named Ansom Stone who quickly takes a liking to Orimar's persona. Jonnit and Gable try to learn more about the manufacturing process for Syndicate Crimson as Orimar tries to do some information gathering of his own. Feed: https://feeds.megaphone.fm/OSPN2193291028
